{"tid":2134260,"cid":10,"subCid":0,"title":"Halo開發組跪低,承認畫面有問題會改善","createTime":"2020-07-31T14:40:50.000Z","updateTime":"2020-08-05T10:21:30.000Z","uid":56731,"like":12,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":9,"replies":[{"pid":"454cd97774072c36d7d234036920eeb3ea1b9446","tid":2134260,"uid":56731,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-31T14:40:50.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/6KymsBx.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F6KymsBx.jpg&h=ece26ab7&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/kGiBguT.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FkGiBguT.gif&h=5ccb84bf&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/spZg0Wz.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FspZg0Wz.jpg&h=95b74ccb&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\nsource:<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.halowaypoint.com/en-us/news/infinite-inquiries\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.halowaypoint.com%2Fen-us%2Fnews%2Finfinite-inquiries&d=dD36If%2FKkPZsb%2F00sEqzOYVlFhl8e2VpHQ9vpRm7Uxg%3D&h=81dbbcf7\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.halowaypoint.com/en-us/news/infinite-inquiries</a><br />\n<br />\n大約內容就係343 Industries回應Halo Infinite畫面問題<br />\n佢哋係art style同visual fidelity方面都收到好多負面回應<br />\n都知道啲角色同物objects望落膠同埋唔夠真,光線呀同俾人見到objects彈出嚟之類嘅問題<br />\n<br />\n佢哋都睇過Digital Foundry段分析片,承認係有改善空間<br />\n不過佢哋都提到個DEMO係幾個禮拜前既野,成品係畫面同系統都有改進"},{"pid":"cd3b5dd649cfd20dc655ff1cb34f7be0fe10f39d","tid":2134260,"uid":3768,"like":10,"dislike":0,"score":10,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-31T14:43:50.000Z","msg":"demo d畫面好似隻game回歸360時代咁<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"88fe8289f2e4a0d30504801cc71190a9a2ecad0b","tid":2134260,"uid":34804,"like":6,"dislike":0,"score":6,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-31T14:44:18.000Z","msg":"都做左成二，三年，仲要趕做果「試玩」<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4259782dc73438fa901234e6bfa0dde4